Package Receipt

Class Receipt

java.lang.Object
Receipt.Receipt
public class Receipt extends Object
Represents a flat booking receipt in the HDB system. It stores details about the applicant, project, and the officer involved.

    • Receipt

      public Receipt(String date, String applicantName, String applicantIc, int applicantAge, MaritalStatus applicantMaritalStatus, String projectId, String projectName, String projectNeighbourhood, String applicationRoomType, String officerName, String date_generated)
      Constructs a new Receipt instance with all relevant booking information.
      Parameters:
      date - the date of booking
      applicantName - the name of the applicant
      applicantIc - the NRIC of the applicant
      applicantAge - the age of the applicant
      applicantMaritalStatus - the marital status of the applicant
      projectId - the ID of the booked project
      projectName - the name of the project
      projectNeighbourhood - the neighborhood where the project is located
      applicationRoomType - the room type applied for
      officerName - the name of the officer who handled the booking
      date_generated - the system-generated date of the receipt
